== 製作 ==
2014年11月，《[[極速秒殺|極速秒殺]]》的續集改由[[丹尼斯·甘塞爾|丹尼斯·甘塞爾]]執導，[[傑森·史塔森|傑森·史塔森]]將回歸飾演亞瑟·畢夏，電影定於2016年推出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=114585 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-06-16 |archive-date=2014-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330131209/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=114585 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年2月4日，[[娜塔莉·伯恩|娜塔莉·伯恩]]加入劇組參與演出<ref name=BurnCast>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=‘Expendables 3′ Actress Natalie Burn Joins Jason Statham in ‘Mechanic: Resurrection’ (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/expendables-3-actress-natalie-burn-joins-jason-statham-in-mechanic-resurrection-exclusive/|accessdate=February 8, 2015|publisher=thewrap.com|date=February 4, 2015|archive-date=2019-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709014012/https://www.thewrap.com/expendables-3-actress-natalie-burn-joins-jason-statham-in-mechanic-resurrection-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
2014年11月4日，電影在[[泰國|泰國]]的[[曼谷|曼谷]]正式拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Afm: Jason Statham’s ‘Mechanic: Resurrection’ Set for Jan. 22, 2016|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jason-statham-mechanic-resurrection-2016-1201351021/|accessdate=November 8, 2014|publisher=variety.com|date=November 8, 2014|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028123101/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/jason-statham-mechanic-resurrection-2016-1201351021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]、[[巴西|巴西]]、[[喬治市|喬治市]]和[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]的[[悉尼|悉尼]]也作為電影的取景地。

== 發行 ==
2014年11月7日，[[獅門影業|獅門影業]]將本片排於2016年1月22日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Lionsgate Dates ‘Criminal’ For Summer; ‘Mechanic’ Sequel Set For 2016, Adds Tommy Lee Jones & Jessica Alba|url=http://deadline.com/2014/11/criminal-mechanic-resurrection-release-date-kevin-costner-jason-statham-1201277849/|accessdate=November 8, 2014|publisher=deadline.com|date=November 7, 2014|archive-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620074238/https://deadline.com/2014/11/criminal-mechanic-resurrection-release-date-kevin-costner-jason-statham-1201277849/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來改至2016年4月15日。2015年8月3日，電影又延期至2016年8月26日<ref name=Aug2015Deadline>{{cite news|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|title=‘Criminal’, ‘Dirty Grandpa’ & ‘Mechanic: Resurrection’ Get New Release Dates|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/criminal-dirty-grandpa-mechanic-resurrection-get-new-release-dates-1201490561/|accessdate=August 4, 2015|work=deadline.com|date=August 3, 2015|archive-date=2015-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212183130/https://deadline.com/2015/08/criminal-dirty-grandpa-mechanic-resurrection-get-new-release-dates-1201490561/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅31%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mechanic_resurrection/ |title=Mechanic: Resurrection (2016) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=August 26, 2016 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204222631/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mechanic_resurrection/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，基於59條評論，平均分為4.45/10，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到38分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mechanic-resurrection|title=Mechanic: Resurrection reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=August 26, 2016|archive-date=2019-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324060226/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/mechanic-resurrection|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.2分，差評居多。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-09-11 |archive-date=2002-09-14 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20020914132118/https://www.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，分析師估計電影於首映週末能從2200間戲院中獲得600至800萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Could Suffocate ‘Suicide Squad’ During Sluggish Summer Weekend: Box Office Preview |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-08-25 |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160825120030/http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首映週末票房收入為750萬美元，位居當週票房排名第五<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Screams $26M+ Opening, Gives Sony 3rd Summer Cash Cow After ‘Sausage Party’, ‘Shallows’: Early Sunday Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|accessdate=August 28, 2016|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210230212/https://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在臺灣，臺北市首映週末票房為1096萬[[新臺幣|新臺幣]]，位居當週冠軍，次週獲440萬元位居第2，僅次於《[[屍速列車|屍速列車]]》，第3週以125萬元的票房位居第五。反應比北美佳。

